
COMMAND                        FUNCTIONALITY 

lsmod                          show loaded kernel modules 

lspci                          show pci devices on system 

lsusb                          to list all usb devices on system 

dmesg                          show kernel messages from boot process onward 

lscpu                          show cpu architecture and other info 

lsblk                          list block devices 

df -h                          show disks and used space in each 

free -h                        display RAM and Swap usage 

inxi                           //learn 

hwinfo                         detailed hardware info 

journalctl                     data from previous boots 
